  m_Name: DemonData_Ekzeema
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: LSG::LSG.DemonData_Ekzeema
  demonName: Ekzeema
  canDateDemonMultipleTimes: 0
  introDialogue: '"You have an inkling that there''s an attractive figure in the
    summoning circle, but they''re a bit hard to make out under the cloud of dust,
    pollen, synthetic fibers, and other less-identifiable particulate swirling around
    them.


    They scratch awkwardly at their neck, belly, upper thigh, and side
    of their face simultaneously while staring at you in shock."'
  minimumPowerLevel: 1
  maximumPowerLevel: 10
  outcome: 
  boon: Gain 1 Rizz the first time you buy a card (repair a page) each round
  bane: For the rest of the game, Lose 1 Sanity each time you play a blue card
  boonBaneDialogue: Ekzeema's Curse caused Sanity loss upon reading this Blue page
  dateOutcome: '"You spend a lovely evening shopping for hypoallergenic skincare
    products that help both of you feel more comfortable being close to each other.


    You
    hold two or three of their hands while checking the pollen count before heading
    out for a nice meal of battered shellfish in soy-peanut sauce."'
  demonSprite: {fileID: -1605223320372934923, guid: 6e32c2cd0cfb7623aa58e9e03c1daeed, type: 3}
